{"tid":2306411,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過戴反con？","createTime":"2020-11-30T11:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T04:43:27.000Z","uid":130593,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ed16f0ecb817b9d17179372a0ea53f5ad14b4cf0","tid":2306411,"uid":130593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"今日去睇眼科除con滴散曈劑，睇眼底<br />\n跟住帶番，點知隻左眼戴反左<br />\n又好奇怪，唔吉眼<br />\n得輕微既異物感同埋睇野濛濛地，等我仲以為係眼滴完藥水，搞到隻con冇咁穩定（我有深散光）同埋以為係散曈劑既side effect<br />\n<br />\n番到屋企，先知戴反左<br />\n都戴反左六個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會對隻眼有咩影響？有冇人知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家暫時冇任何野"},{"pid":"477d00639c8779ff09f6665c4200067502f453af","tid":2306411,"uid":352867,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"我一帶反左就會勁吉眼<br />\n眨眼眨到標晒眼水 所以未試過帶反<br />\n你唯有下次小心啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201ef006cee648c77524eba035cd4a23d5d0066a","tid":2306411,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T18:46:35.000Z","msg":"試過戴反左之後搭飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />途中好吉眼<br />\n落左機頂唔順即刻換第副先知自己戴反左<br />\n依家好彩未話有d咩事"},{"pid":"05717677a3832e2e10f748d99aba2d0b1fe21c86","tid":2306411,"uid":130593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201ef006cee648c77524eba035cd4a23d5d0066a","tid":2306411,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T18:46:35.000Z","msg":"試過戴反左之後搭飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />途中好吉眼<br />\n落左機頂唔順即刻換第副先知自己戴反左<br />\n依家好彩未話有d咩事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T00:29:27.000Z","msg":"你果次幾多個鐘？"},{"pid":"118b3824940772cf3a8bdf587ab00f867dd9f430","tid":2306411,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05717677a3832e2e10f748d99aba2d0b1fe21c86","tid":2306411,"uid":130593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201